name: London IP
tag_list: patent, trademark, attorney, attorneys, agent, agents, lawyer, lawyers
overview:
London IP is a firm of patent attorneys and trademark attorneys providing help with patents, trademarks, registered designs and copyright in the UK, Europe and internationally.

London IP attorneys represent clients before the UKIPO, EPO and OHIM.

London IP patent attorneys advise on patentability of inventions, draft and file patent applications, prosecute the applications to grant and assist with post-grant patent disputes.

London IP trademark attorneys advise on registrability of trademarks, and assist clients in obtaining, enforcing and defending trademark registrations.

London IP offers a free consultation on any intellectual property manner.
